<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.7">
<l>aṇṭat tamarar perumā ṉāḻiyā ṉiṉṟeṉ makaḷai</l>
<l>paṇṭap paḻippukkaḷ collip paricaṟa vāṇṭiṭuṅ kolō</l>
<l>koṇṭu kuṭivāḻkkai vāḻntu kōvalap paṭṭaṅ kavittu</l>
<l>paṇṭai maṇāṭṭimār muṉṉē pātukā valvaikkuṅ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Now, will the Lord of the heavenly immortals, the discus-bearer,</l>
<l rend="indent">disparage my daughter’s belongings</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] receive her without honour?</l>
<l>Or will [he], having accepted [her], live a prosperous family life,</l>
<l rend="indent">crowning [her] queen of the cowherds</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] provide protection [for her]</l>
<l rend="indent">in front of [his] previous brides?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
